{"parse":{"title":"Butane/es","pageid":3052,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>6-3-350</b>\n</p><p><big><big><big>Butano</big></big></big>\n</p><p><br>\nCombustible de hidrocarburo, C4H10, gas a temperaturas  y presi\u00f3n atmosf\u00e9rica normales. Dado que posee un punto de ebullici\u00f3n de 1<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"4723eb5aa8b0cd28c7e09433839b8fae\">&deg;</span> grado Celsius a presi\u00f3n atmosf\u00e9rica no puede ser utilizado en climas fr\u00edos como combustible gaseoso.\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p>Nota: El butano est\u00e1 disponible comercialmente bajo varios nombres.\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Butane\" title=\"Butane\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n\u00a0\u2022\u00a0<span lang=\"es\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">espa\u00f1ol</a></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"4723eb5aa8b0cd28c7e09433839b8fae\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>degree\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615104422\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.028 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.037 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 69/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 911/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 104/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 3/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.930      1 -total\n 76.31%    9.104      1 Template:Languages\n 49.08%    5.856      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n 22.77%    2.716      1 Template:IALAFooter\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:3052-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615104422 and revision id 8553. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"Alphabetical_Index"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_1970-89_Edition"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Indice_alfabeto_Espa\u00f1ol"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_2018_Revision"}]}}